==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Promissory
<hw>Prom"is*so*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Containing a
promise or binding declaration of something to be done or
forborne.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Promissory note</b></col> <fld>(Law)</fld>, <cd>a written
promise to pay to some person named, and at a time specified therein, or
on demand, or at sight, a certain sum of money, absolutely and at all
events; -- frequently called a <altname>note of hand</altname>.</cd>
<rj><au>Kent. Byles. Story.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Promont</ent>⟦br⟧
